data.description:
(CURRENT APPRAISAL ON FILE.)
Beautiful home located in quiet neighborhood. Great location to RAFB, Schools, Shopping. This home has many upgrades, granite countertops, tile and wood flooring. There are two Master bedrooms one upstairs and one downstairs. Each bedroom has large walk-in closets, and two large walk-in attic storage spaces. In ground saltwater pool with new pool liner installed 3/2019. In ground sprinkler system with new control panel. Screened back porch with all the furniture and pool furniture included. Some appliances and furniture are included with the house. Nice large privacy fenced back yard. These pictures really do not do the house justice. Must see to appreciate.
data.whatILove: You have some really Great neighbors here and it is a good place to raise a family. It is very peaceful and you have a lot of privacy in the back yard to just kick back and relax in the pool or sit on the back screened porch and unwind with some TV or surround sound music. You won’t be disappointed.!
